## Bug fixes

- Fixed IL CMS vendors appearing with TX market badge in Error Catalog.
- Fixed simple envelope format (`{ eventType, entities: [...] }`) always routing to TX regardless of entity types.
- Fixed pre-v2.1 history runs for IL vendors permanently showing as TX in the Error Catalog.

---

## Unchanged in v2.4

- All TX OCA validation rules (schema v3.0.0)
- All IL AOIC validation rules (schema v3.1.0, 37 entity types)
- Full IL envelope format detection (unchanged — was already correct)
- Array and single-entity IL detection (unchanged — fixed in v2.3)
- Error Catalog tab, Error Library search, nav structure
- Ctrl+Enter / Cmd+Enter shortcut
- History / Export — all export formats, Save All, Import, 7-day TTL

