## Deployment

Replace `CATCH.html` in the repository root. No other file changes. The market correction for previously stored history takes effect immediately on next Error Catalog refresh — no history clear needed.

```
gh release create v2.4 CATCH.html \
  --title "CATCH v2.4" \
  --notes-file CATCH_v2.4_Release_Notes.md
```
